{"tid":915681,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"廣東話討論：成日聽人講「貼錢買難受」，有無人覺得「係貼錢買爛壽」至係原本嘅講法呢？","createTime":"2018-11-25T07:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T07:24:32.000Z","uid":54133,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"237b5d2fba4ef93edecc1250fbac6a88f859b742","tid":915681,"uid":54133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T07:12:47.000Z","msg":"成日聽人講「貼錢買難受」，<br />\n不過有無人覺得「貼錢買<strong>爛壽</strong>」至係原來嘅講法？<br />\n<br />\n雖然我見中大個網咁寫⋯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/25/144941_a8f3eaf34590bf1320f1d0e9dfd1e45e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F25%2F144941_a8f3eaf34590bf1320f1d0e9dfd1e45e.png&h=fc937cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以我理解「壽」係指「壽木」，<br />\n「爛壽」即係「爛嘅棺材」⋯<br />\n「貼錢買爛壽」即係畀咗錢點知仲買咗副爛嘅棺材⋯⋯有死唔眼閉、付出咗點知無好下場/收獲嘅意思。<br />\n<br />\n因為無人知「爛壽」點解，慢慢變成「難受」，而又解得通咁。<br />\n<br />\n利申：無reference，純粹討論吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397062b29cd8a77438ce31584ecc1a043145090b","tid":915681,"uid":59922,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T07:15:43.000Z","msg":"老陳<br />\n老「診」<br />\n<br />\n有個人叫我<br />\n有個「忍」叫我<br />\n<br />\n得我自己一個人咋<br />\n得我自己一個「因」咋"},{"pid":"2ae8f28c13b959411908d985acf5cf31fbcd52f7","tid":915681,"uid":25108,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T07:15:58.000Z","msg":"難受有咩問題<br />\n本身都有呢個詞"},{"pid":"f285664448f308b4324621c15ff5661b3d42112b","tid":915681,"uid":72968,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T07:16:53.000Z","msg":"係又點唔係又點<br />\n是撚但啦屌"},{"pid":"8ae70f7939dac891ac2db1b03886f62ebdbe86cc","tid":915681,"uid":62487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T07:24:32.000Z","msg":"壽-&gt;棺材<br />\n難-&gt;災難<br />\n邊個近d?"}]}